![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580661-5263.jpeg)

[ ![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580661-5263.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580661-5263.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580645-5020.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580645-5020.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580645-1610.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580645-1610.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580646-5970.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580646-5970.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580645-6959.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580645-6959.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580646-3161.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580646-3161.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580646-2997.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580646-2997.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580647-9059.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580647-9059.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-12T17-39-05-03-00/630_360_1686580647-4597.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686580647-4597.jpeg)

