[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-06-12T82-00-00-04-00/foto-4-6-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/foto-4-6.jpg)

[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-06-12T82-00-00-04-00/foto-5-4-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/foto-5-4.jpg)

[![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-06-12T82-00-00-04-00/foto-6-5-150x150.jpg)](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/foto-6-5.jpg)

